    "1643623434867f098c": {
      "type": "accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "16436234342ee419df-0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Payment options",
            "description": "<p>At “Company name”, we accept all major forms of credit cards, as well as several other forms of payment: 💳<br/><br/>• American Express<br/>• Discover<br/>• MasterCard<br/>• Visa<br/>• PayPal<br/>• Gift Card<br/><br/>We do not accept the following forms of payment:<br/><br/>• CODs<br/>• Layaway plans<br/>• Merchandise Return Cards<br/><br/>Important Payment Information:<br/><br/>• Credit cards are not charged until order products are shipped.<br/>• Some debit and bank check cards may reflect deduction of funds immediately upon order. This is an authorization only. Funds will be collected by “Company name” upon shipment of products.<br/>• For your security, your billing name and address must match that of the credit card used for payment. We reserve the right to cancel any order that does not match these criteria.<br/>• Merchandise Return Cards are valid for in-store purchases only.</p>"
          }
        },
        "e262f4a7-2dfa-4726-93ea-f5997d7bdc5b": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer discounts?",
            "description": "<p>Unfortunately, we do not offer discounts on our products at this time.</p>"
          }
        },
        "16436234342ee419df-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Gift cards 🎁",
            "description": "<p>Let's Get Started<br/><br/>• Shop online at “Company name” and add products to your shopping cart.<br/>• When you're ready to check out, go to your shopping cart and proceed to checkout.<br/>• Enter your gift card number and unique PIN (codes are case sensitive) in section 4: payment details.<br/>• Please save your gift card for future use if it covers the full amount of the transaction. If your gift card only covers a portion of the transaction, an additional form of payment is required.<br/>• If you have a gift card that does not have a PIN, it cannot be redeemed online and can only be redeemed at a “Company name” retail store. In order to use your gift card online, your remaining balance can be transferred to a new gift card at your local “Company name”.<br/>• When making a purchase online at “Company name”, you may redeem up to 5 gift cards per order.<br/>• Gift cards are not accepted for auto ship orders.<br/>• Purchases of gift cards are not eligible for Treats points.<br/>• Merchandise Return cards are valid in-store only and cannot be used to purchase items online.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
